item.description:
@god_of_ikiliki wrote:

Right Click on ur Compile.bat
Click “Edit”
Now notepad will open
Delete all and add:

@echo off title [name] Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java pause
